        <div class="social-author__bio"><p>
	David Pierce (
	<a href="https://twitter.com/pierce" target="_blank">@pierce</a>) is Protocol's editor at large. Prior to joining Protocol, he was a columnist at The Wall Street Journal, a senior writer with Wired, and deputy editor at The Verge. He owns all the phones.
