        <a class="social-author__name" href="https://www.protocol.com/u/emilybirnbaum" data-type="text">Emily Birnbaum</a>
        
        <div class="social-author__bio"><p>
	Emily Birnbaum (
	<a href="https://twitter.com/birnbaum_e" target="_blank">@birnbaum_e</a>) is a tech policy reporter with Protocol. Her coverage focuses on the U.S. government's attempts to regulate one of the most powerful industries in the world, with a focus on antitrust, privacy and politics. Previously, she worked as a tech policy reporter with The Hill after spending several months as a breaking news reporter. She is a Bethesda, Maryland native and proud Kenyon College alumna.
</p></div>
        
